{"tid":2274772,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"美國政府宣布不再把東突厥斯坦伊斯蘭運動列為恐怖組織","createTime":"2020-11-06T15:56:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-06T16:13:35.000Z","uid":44209,"like":13,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"2fb8b5dfb753fb2823297fc8af9516e8c9663549","tid":2274772,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T15:56:51.000Z","msg":"美國政府宣布，不再把東突厥斯坦伊斯蘭運動列為恐怖組織。<br />\n<br />\n美國國務院11月5日在聯邦公報（Federal Register）上發布的通知做如上表述。<br />\n<br />\n美國國務卿蓬佩奧在通知中說，根據《移民和國籍法》(INA) 212(a)(B)(II)修訂條款的授權，撤銷東突厥斯坦伊斯蘭運動（Eastern Turkistan Islamic Movement）的&ldquo;恐怖組織&rdquo;的定列。<br />\n<br />\n維基百科說，美國等國是在2001年9月11日恐怖攻擊發生之後將東突厥斯坦伊斯蘭運動列為恐怖組織的。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.voacantonese.com/amp/xj-etim-delisted-as-terriorist-org-20201106-ry/5650556.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.voacantonese.com%2Famp%2Fxj-etim-delisted-as-terriorist-org-20201106-ry%2F5650556.html&d=q9TyM%2Fq5ITgKOQyjXL1c9iHJFIlRN37b%2BuZTNWj4Tkw%3D&h=da19e08f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.voacantonese.com/amp/xj-etim-delisted-as-terriorist-org-20201106-ry/5650556.html</a>"},{"pid":"3a9f8b8a0fcf00e698a45dc3c7c05ddfcb4f7774","tid":2274772,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T15:59:18.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"a34ce135b4932642182f598e31e7052229b5ae89","tid":2274772,"uid":179649,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T15:59:57.000Z","msg":"將港共支共納入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a86c98e8aaa90c729bb44f29a542d3b376dea224","tid":2274772,"uid":54373,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"2fb8b5dfb753fb2823297fc8af9516e8c9663549","tid":2274772,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T15:56:51.000Z","msg":"美國政府宣布，不再把東突厥斯坦伊斯蘭運動列為恐怖組織。<br />\n<br />\n美國國務院11月5日在聯邦公報（Federal Register）上發布的通知做如上表述。<br />\n<br />\n美國國務卿蓬佩奧在通知中說，根據《移民和國籍法》(INA) 212(a)(B)(II)修訂條款的授權，撤銷東突厥斯坦伊斯蘭運動（Eastern Turkistan Islamic Movement）的&ldquo;恐怖組織&rdquo;的定列。<br />\n<br />\n維基百科說，美國等國是在2001年9月11日恐怖攻擊發生之後將東突厥斯坦伊斯蘭運動列為恐怖組織的。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.voacantonese.com/amp/xj-etim-delisted-as-terriorist-org-20201106-ry/5650556.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.voacantonese.com%2Famp%2Fxj-etim-delisted-as-terriorist-org-20201106-ry%2F5650556.html&d=q9TyM%2Fq5ITgKOQyjXL1c9iHJFIlRN37b%2BuZTNWj4Tkw%3D&h=da19e08f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.voacantonese.com/amp/xj-etim-delisted-as-terriorist-org-20201106-ry/5650556.html</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T16:01:37.000Z","msg":"可以做西北面戰線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a33036ae5fd6711dc4a6f1c0d3d22bbd9a6865f","tid":2274772,"uid":92376,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T16:02:03.000Z","msg":"一個幾月有咩好做盡做啦"},{"pid":"fc0e902aace9be67ac444a6e89030b74470ca992","tid":2274772,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1a33036ae5fd6711dc4a6f1c0d3d22bbd9a6865f","tid":2274772,"uid":92376,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T16:02:03.000Z","msg":"一個幾月有咩好做盡做啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T16:02:34.000Z","msg":"快啲打柒中國啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40f5ff0317ac21ad41955bf1ad779f6663027967","tid":2274772,"uid":51583,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T16:03:31.000Z","msg":"轉比POPO得嗎?"},{"pid":"657becfb19ce6bb3d4545e7175d8877321563a15","tid":2274772,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"40f5ff0317ac21ad41955bf1ad779f6663027967","tid":2274772,"uid":51583,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T16:03:31.000Z","msg":"轉比POPO得嗎?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T16:04:56.000Z","msg":"ＰＯＰＯ係好人黎<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sVY39Re.jpg\" data-thu